column1: #Text=Egyptian archaeologist finds artifacts which may lead to Cleopatra 's tomb
#Text=, Egypt ' s pre-eminent archaeologist , revealed the first ancient artifacts which may lead to the discovery of Cleopatra and Marc Antony ' s resting place .
#Text=The expedition has found amulet s , 22 bronze coins cast with Cleopatra 's image and her name , a royal statue , an alabaster mask resembling Marc Antony , and a statue bust of Cleopatra .
